{"url": "https://www.ics.uci.edu/~shantas/", "content": "<html>\n<head>\n\t<!-- Site Title -->\n\t<title>Shantanu Sharma - Home Page</title>\n\t\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"css/bootstrap.css\">\n\t\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"css/main.css\">\n\t\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/w3css/4/w3.css\">\n</head>\n\t\n<body>\t\n\t<header id=\"header\">\n\t    <div class=\"container main-menu\">\n\t    \t<div class=\"row align-items-center justify-content-between\">\n\t\t        <font size=\"5\" color =\"#1C64DD\"> Shantanu Sharma</b></font>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"home-about-right\">\n\t\t\t\t\tPostdoc, Computer Science <BR>\n\t\t\t\t\tUniversity of California, Irvine, USA.\n\t\t\t    </div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n<!--nav bar -->\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"w3-bar w3-light-blue\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~shantas/\" class=\"w3-bar-item w3-button w3-hover-gray\">Home</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~shantas/publications.html\" class=\"w3-bar-item w3-button w3-hover-gray\">Publications</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~shantas/teaching.html\" class=\"w3-bar-item w3-button w3-hover-gray\">Teaching</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~shantas/cv.html\" class=\"w3-bar-item w3-button w3-hover-gray\">CV</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~shantas/other.html\" class=\"w3-bar-item w3-button w3-hover-gray\">Pics</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"dropdown\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<button class=\"dropbtn \">Others </button>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"dropdown-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~shantas/narratives.html\">Narratives</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~shantas/software.html\">Software</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">Links</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div> \n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"logo-align\">\n<A HREF=\"https://twitter.com/tweet_shantanu\"><IMG SRC=\"HTML/images/twitter.png\" WIDTH=\"35\" HEIGHT=\"37\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"\"></A> \n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\t\t\t\t\t\n<A HREF=\"http://www.researchgate.net/profile/Shantanu_Sharma2/publications\"><IMG SRC=\"HTML/images/ResearchGate_Logo.png\" WIDTH=\"75\" HEIGHT=\"37\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"\"></A>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n<A HREF=\"http://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/s/Sharma_0001:Shantanu\"><IMG SRC=\"HTML/images/dblp_logo.png\" WIDTH=\"60\" HEIGHT=\"37\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"\"></A>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n<A HREF=\"http://www.slideshare.net/ShantanuSharma12/presentations\"><IMG SRC=\"HTML/images/slideshare.jpg\" WIDTH=\"50\" HEIGHT=\"37\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"\"></A>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n<A HREF=\"https://www.facebook.com/shantanu.sharma.bgu\"><IMG SRC=\"HTML/images/facebook.jpg\" WIDTH=\"37\" HEIGHT=\"37\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"\"></A> \n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n<a href=\"http://www.clustrmaps.com/map/ics.uci.edu/~shantas/\" title=\"Visitor Map for ics.uci.edu/~shantas/\"><img src=\"//www.clustrmaps.com/map_v2.png?u=qd8r&d=MXYTiVS0MLovte1-oJ7Mdl71MTf1EwYNF8oGxi48kxQ\" WIDTH=\"37\" HEIGHT=\"37\"/></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<!--nav bar -->\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</header>\n\t\t\t  \n\t\t\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\n\t<section class=\"home-about-area section-gap\">\n\t\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"row align-items-center justify-content-between\">\n\t\t\t\t<img class=\"\" src=\"HTML/images/ShantanuSharma.jpg\" height=\"442\" width=\"300\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"home-about-right\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h1 class=\"h1-heading\" >Personal Details</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class= \"paragraph\">\n\n\nI am a Post-Doc in <A class=\"hlink\" HREF=\"http://www.cs.uci.edu/\">Department of Computer Science</A> at the <A class=\"hlink\"  HREF=\"http://uci.edu/\">University of California, Irvine</A>, USA. \n\n\n<br>\n<br>\n<b><FONT SIZE=\"\" COLOR=\"#3300FF\">Post-Doc advisor:</FONT></b> <A class=\"hlink\" HREF=\"https://www.ics.uci.edu/~sharad/\">Prof. Sharad Mehrotra</A>  \n\n\n\n<br>\n<br>\nI completed my Ph.D. in <A HREF=\"http://www.cs.bgu.ac.il/\" class=\"hlink\">Department of Computer Science</A> at <A class=\"hlink\"  HREF=\"http://in.bgu.ac.il/en/Pages/default.aspx\">Ben-Gurion University of the Negev</A>, <A class=\"hlink\"  HREF=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beersheba\">Beersheva</A>, <A HREF=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Israel\">Israel</A>.  \n<br>I am blessed to become an academic son of <A class=\"hlink\"  HREF=\"http://www.cs.bgu.ac.il/~dolev/\">Prof. Shlomi Dolev</A> and getting guidance from <A class=\"hlink\"  HREF=\"http://infolab.stanford.edu/~ullman/\"> Prof. Jeffrey Ullman</A> during my Ph.D. work as well as in present. \n\n<br><br>\n<b><FONT SIZE=\"\" COLOR=\"#3300FF\">The title of Ph.D. thesis:</FONT></b> Replication Aspects in Distributed Systems.\n<br> Abstract and thesis presentation slides are available <a class=\"hlink\" href=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~shantas/cv.html\">here</a>.\n\t\t\t\t\n<br>\n<br>\n<b><FONT SIZE=\"\" COLOR=\"#3300FF\">Research interests:</FONT></b> Big-data processing, computing models for MapReduce, security-privacy in MapReduce and Hadoop, distributed computing, and mobile computing.\n\n\n<br><br>\n\n<b><FONT SIZE=\"\" COLOR=\"#3300FF\">Email:</FONT></b> shantanu.sharma@uci.edu, to_shantanusharma@ieee.org\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t</div>\t\n\t</section>\n</body>\n</html>", "encoding": "ascii"}